  "keyFeatures": [
    "Live camera feed monitoring with real-time frame streaming via WebSocket",
    "AI-powered motion detection and object tracking (YOLO + ByteTrack)",
    "Hot-reloadable detection rules and configurable presets",
    "Forensic event trail with full audit log of all user and system actions",
    "Role-based access control (Viewer, Operator, Analyst, Admin, Super Admin)",
    "Multi-factor authentication: TOTP, passkeys (WebAuthn), and OAuth SSO (Google, GitHub, Microsoft)",
    "Event review workflow with severity triage (confirmed, false positive, escalated)",
    "GDPR-compliant data export and right-to-erasure (pseudonymization)"
  ],
